			<description><![CDATA[<p>
Create.net is constantly growing and evolving and you&#39;ll find our offices are a fun (but also challenging) focused working environment.</p>
<p>
We&#39;re looking for an enthusiastic and talented individual to join our team. Great communication skills and team collaboration are a must and we&#39;ll expect you to be someone that loves a challenge! Being flexible and willing to go that extra mile are also important to us and you&#39;ll be keen to pitch in and help others when necessary.</p>
<p>
The position will be based in our offices in the modern and eco-friendly Westergate Business Centre, off the Lewes Road, Brighton.</p>
<p>
The purpose of the role is to provide our growing customer base with excellent, informed customer service and support our members to build successful online businesses.</p>
<p>
We are looking for an enthusiastic and self-motivated individual to join our friendly Customer Services team. The role will be customer service-based, with the opportunity to express your creative side whilst providing support to thousands of businesses.</p>
<p>
A good understanding of the Internet and previous experience in a customer services or customer facing role is essential.</p>
<p>
Our company has a very hands-on approach and we are constantly growing and evolving, so the person we are looking for will enjoy getting involved and bringing new ideas to the team.</p>
<p>
<strong>Daily Duties:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Helping customers with their enquiries</li>
<li>
Supporting our current and potential customers</li>
<li>
Taking an active role in our community forums</li>
<li>
Developing our support areas and FAQ bases</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Essential Skills:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Fluent English and strong written skills</li>
<li>
Enthusiastic and out-going personality</li>
<li>
Confidence to work with minimal supervision</li>
<li>
Good computer skills including typing</li>
<li>
Interest in the Internet and business online</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Desirable Skills:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Experience with building a website and understanding how it works</li>
<li>
Customer service experience and skills</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Additional Information:</strong></p>
<p>
Salary based on skills and experience. &nbsp;</p>
